Registration Fees:

Important Notes:

  • Extra Page Charges: Papers exceeding 12 pages (in the specified Springer format) will incur additional charges: INR 500 per page for Indian authors and USD 10 per page for foreign authors.
  • SCRS Membership: Participants are encouraged to join the Soft Computing Research Society (SCRS) to benefit from reduced registration fees.
  • Registration Includes: The registration fee covers online conference proceedings, presentation at the conference, attendance at all sessions, and keynote talks.
  • No Refunds: The registration fee is non-refundable; cancellations are not permitted once the fee is paid.
